---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  locale="en"
  title="Terms of Service | Hooosberg"
  description="Terms for using the Hooosberg website, including informational content, external links, and open-source notes."
  canonicalPath="/en/terms"
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <p class="hero-kicker">Legal</p>
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="legal-page__updated">Last updated: 2026-06-21</p>

    <p>
      By using hooosberg.com, you understand and accept these terms. The site provides public product pages, build diaries, AI tool notes,
      course information, and contact links.
    </p>

    <h2>Informational content</h2>
    <p>
      Content is based on real product work, personal experience, and public research. It is for information and learning, not legal, financial,
      medical, or other professional advice. Product availability, platform policies, and pricing can change over time.
    </p>

    <h2>Intellectual property and open source</h2>
    <p>
      The website source can be viewed on GitHub. Unless otherwise stated, text, product names, icons, screenshots, brand assets, and third-party marks
      remain owned by their respective rights holders. Use repository code under the license and notes provided in the repository.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      The site may link to third-party platforms such as GitHub, App Store, YouTube, X, Bilibili, Telegram, Google, and Cloudflare.
      We do not control their content, privacy practices, or availability.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      The site is provided as is. We try to keep the content accurate and available, but we do not guarantee that it will always be complete,
      error-free, or uninterrupted.
    </p>

    <h2>Updates</h2>
    <p>
      These terms may be updated when the website, analytics setup, or operating model changes.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
